Package Services.Input

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EventInput
    A class that contains all of the information needed for an event input
    Fields: authToken, eventID, userName
    FillInput
    A class that holds the data for the fill service Inherits from Input Fields: generations - the number of generations to fill, default being 4
    Input
    An input super class.
    LoadEvent
    A class that contains a string representation of an event Only used internally
    LoadInput
    A class that contains all of the information needed for the Load Service.
    LoadPerson
    A string representation of a person
    LoginInput
    A class that contains all of the input information needed for a user to login.
    PersonInput
    A class that holds all of the information needed for the person service
    Fields: userName, personID
    RegisterInput
    A class that contains all of the information needed for a user to register.
